The paper focuses on image retrieval using deep hashing methods, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves using convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and semantic information (cs.AI) to guide the training of the network. Additionally, the paper evaluates the method on large-scale datasets (cs.IR) and conducts experiments on fine-grained classification (cs.MM).
